{"id":299290432,"lang":"python","time":"1 year, 5 months","timestamp":1580579552,"status_display":"Time Limit Exceeded","runtime":"N/A","url":"/submissions/detail/299290432/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"3Sum","memory":"N/A","code":"from collections import defaultdict\nclass Solution:\n    def threeSum(self, nums):\n        N = len(nums)\n        ans_set = set()\n        for i in xrange(N):\n            target = -nums[i]\n            val2idx = defaultdict(list)\n            for j in xrange(N):\n                if j==i:\n                    continue\n                val = target - nums[j]\n                val2idx[val].append(j)\n            for k in xrange(N):\n                if k==i:\n                    continue\n                if nums[k] in val2idx.keys():\n                    idices = val2idx[nums[k]]\n                    for idx in idices:\n                        if idx==k:\n                            continue\n                        ans = sorted([nums[i], nums[k], nums[idx]])\n                        ans_set.add(tuple(ans))\n        res = []\n        for ans in ans_set:\n            res.append(list(ans))\n        return res\n","compare_result":"","title_slug":"3sum"}
